[{"type":"{{","value":[["pagebanner"],["Pagebanner default.jpg"]]},"\n\n",{"type":"'''","value":["Pottes"]}," is  a small ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Belgium"],["Belgian"]]}," village in the ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Celles"],["Celles Region"]]}," which is in the North of the Province of ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Hainaut"]]},", not so far from ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Flanders"]]},".\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["Understand"]},"\n",{"type":"==","value":["Get in"]},"\n",{"type":"===","value":["By train"]},"\nThere is no station at Pottes. The nearest stations are ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Tournai"]]}," (16 km from Pottes) and Avelgem (7 km from Pottes)\n\n",{"type":"===","value":["By the bus"]},"\nThere are two buses that go through Pottes: one on the morning and one on the afternoon\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["Get around"]},"\nPottes is a village so there is no difficulty to go round in it.\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["See"]},"\n",{"type":"==","value":["Do"]},"\nThere is lot of possibilities of walks in the surroundings of Pottes and you can do it by foot,by bike or by horse. Not far from Pottes you find the \"Mont Saint-Aubert\" and the \"Mont de L'enclus\"\" that are touristic and offer good walks ( there is possibility to drink and eat there)\n\n",{"type":"===","value":[" Local festivals or celebrations "]},"\nIt exists two local celebrations called \"fair\"\n\n",{"type":"*","value":[" The first is \" The small fair\": it takes place on the Sunday which follows the Saint Jean in June and so it takes place in spring"]},"\n",{"type":"*","value":[" The second is \" The big fair\": it takes place in September at the same time as the fair of Tournai. It lasts 3 days."]},"\nThere is also the agricultural fair which take place in mid-September.\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["Buy"]},"\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["Eat"]},"\n",{"type":"*","value":[" ",{"type":"{{","value":[["eat"],["name=Farm Ruisseau"],["alt="],["url="],["email="],["address=Au Petit Marais 16"],["lat="],["long="]